        <A.Title>Altering admin permissions</A.Title>
        <A.Description>This user is assigned to an
          <Hds::RichTooltip @isInline={{true}} as |RT|>
            <RT.ToggleInfoText>admin role</RT.ToggleInfoText>
            <RT.PopoverContent>
              Admin role enables a couple of pretty cool features and permissions within the app. For details on what an
